<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>霓虹工具箱 | 多链探针</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, #0a0f1a, #03060c);
            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem;
            color: #0ff;
        }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; text-shadow: 0 0 8px #0ff; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
        .subtitle { color: #7cf9ff; font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .tools-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .tool-card {
            background: rgba(8,16,24,0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border: 1px solid #0ff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: block;
        }
        .tool-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); box-shadow: 0 0 20px #0ff; border-color: #ff00cc; }
        .tool-card h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #0ff; }
        .tool-card p { color: #9effff; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #0ff6; border-top: 1px dashed #0ff3; padding-top: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
        a { text-decoration: none; }
        @media (max-width: 700px) { body { padding: 1rem; } h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; } .tool-card h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>>_ 霓虹工具箱</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">⚡ 多链探针 | 数据本地存储 | 持续更新</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tools-grid">
        <a href="/usdt" class="tool-card">
            <h2>💰 USDT 地址管理器</h2>
            <p>查询 TRC20 / ERC20 余额及交易记录 | 多地址管理 | 数据独立</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/hacker" class="tool-card">
            <h2>🔧 黑客工具包</h2>
            <p>IP查询 | 端口扫描(模拟) | 密码强度检测 | 加密编解码</p>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        ⚡ 工具运行于免费云服务 | 15分钟无访问自动休眠<br>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>